Class OTLSpanContextImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sc.hm.otl.core.impl.OTLSpanContextImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OTLSpanContext, io.opentracing.SpanContext

    public class OTLSpanContextImpl
extends Object
implements OTLSpanContext
    Concrete class to represent the span context. A span context is an immutable object, which means once created with the traceId, spanId and parentSpanId, their values cannot be changed.
    Author:
    Sudiptasish Chanda
